        %tr
          %td{:bgcolor => "#f6dcc6", :style => "border-left:3px solid #aa4d49; border-right:3px solid #aa4d49;"}
            %p{:style => "font-size: 16px; color:#68A7BF; font-weight:bold; text-align:left;  padding-left: 20px; padding-top: 10px;"}
              Dear #{@student.full_name},
            %p{:style => "font-size: 12px; color:#666; text-align:left; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;"}
              It gives us immense pleasure to announce the beginning of a new era of communication between us.
              As of today we begin a constant web presence at 
